v1.2.1 (2024-02-5)

- Update LICENSE and README files

  - Updated LICENSE file with the latest version information and year.
  - Improved the README with clearer installation instructions, project setup, and contributing guidelines.

- Bug Fixes

  - Fixed issue with incorrect error handling in the login process (`274`).
  - Resolved memory leak in `emailService` module when handling large payloads.

- Enhancements

  - Optimized database queries for better performance in high-traffic scenarios.
  - Improved API response time by caching frequently accessed data.
  - Updated project dependencies to their latest stable versions to ensure better compatibility.

- Documentation

  - Added more detailed API documentation in the README (`/docs/api.md`).
  - Clarified instructions for setting up the project for local development.
  - Added troubleshooting section for common setup issues.

- Refactoring

  - Refactored the `authService` module for better readability and maintainability.
  - Modularized the `email` functionality into its own package for easier updates and scalability.

- Other Changes
  - Updated error logging format for better debugging (`logger` improvements).
  - Improved the test suite with new unit tests for the `userController`.

v1.2.0 (2024-01-15)

- New Features

  - Added support for multi-language user interface (`265`).
  - Introduced new `notifications` feature for sending alerts to users (`251`).

- Bug Fixes
  - Fixed a bug where user data was not properly saved to the database in edge cases.

v1.1.1 (2023-11-10)

- Bug Fixes

  - Fixed issue causing some `POST` requests to fail intermittently in production.

- Improvement
  - Enhanced validation on form inputs in the user registration process.

v1.1.0 (2023-09-18)

- New Features

  - Added support for exporting user data to CSV format (`239`).
  - Implemented basic email notification system for user actions (`225`).

- Bug Fixes
  - Fixed issue where app crashed if no internet connection was available.
- Documentation
  - Updated README with new setup instructions and feature documentation.
